Actually, UnderT, its the more accurate one. Zardus and Wolfgang did
attempt to make a new faction before Zardus was taken over by the Vok,
but it was under Vok influence that he finally convinced Wolfgang to
start the Alliance with him.

::Havoc/FZ::

The doors to the CR chamber are opened from the outside, and Havoc
enters, followed by FZ. FZ looked exactly like Zardus used to, so
Wolfgang should recognize him.

"Here he is, sir," Havoc says to FZ, motioning to Wolfgang. FZ nods
and approaches.

"Welcome back to the Alliance, Wolfgang," he says, his eyes showing
his amusement. The former co-leader of the Alliance now weaponless in
a CR room.
